Date: Sunday 3rd November 2013
Time: 14:20-17:30

Live coverage of the final day's action from the opening round of the 2013-14 World Cup series from the Manchester Velodrome, plus a look back at the event's highlights so far. With the women's omnium on Sunday's schedule, Britain's Laura Trott could strut her stuff in one of two events she won Olympic gold in last summer.
